<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Neighbourhood Market</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial;
      margin: 0;
      background: #f5f5f5;
    }
    header {
      background: #111;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .container {
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    button {
      padding: 10px;
      border: none;
      background: black;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>🏘️ Neighbourhood Market</h1>
  <p>Buy & Sell within your community</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <div class="card">
    <h2>📱 Get the App</h2>
    <p>Use our mobile app to list items, make offers, and chat instantly.</p>
    <p><b>Run using Expo:</b> npx expo start --tunnel</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🛍️ Example Listings</h2>
    <p>Cycle - ₹3000</p>
    <p>Study Table - ₹1500</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>💡 How it works</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>List items</li>
      <li>Receive offers</li>
      <li>Accept and sell</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
